column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID,round(p.ra,#) as ra,round(p.dec,#) as dec,round(p.u,#) as PhotoOb_u,round(p.g,#) as PhotoOb_g,round(p.r,#) as PhotoOb_r, round(p.i,#) as PhotoOb_i,round(p.err_u,#) as err_u, round(p.err_g,#) as err_g, round(p.err_r,#) as err_r, round(P.err_i,#) as err_i, round(modelMag_u,#) as modelMag_u,round(modelMag_g,#) as modelMag_g, round(modelMag_r,#) as modelMag_r, round(modelMag_i,#) as modelMag_i,round(p.modelMagErr_u,#) as modelMagErr_u,round(p.modelMagErr_g,#) as modelMagErr_g, round(p.modelMagErr_r,#) as modelMagErr_r, round(p.modelMagErr_i,#) as modelMagErr_i,round(p.z,#) as PhotoObj_z,round(p.Err_z,#) as PhotoObj_Err_z, p.type, /*specObj table parameters*/ s.specobjid, s.class, s.subClass, round(s.z,#) as spec_redshift, round(s.zErr,#) as spec_redshift_Err,round(s.zWarning,#) as Spec_redshift_Warning, /* Photomtric redshift table parameters*/ round(pz.z,#) As Photoz_z, round(pz.zErr,#) AS Photoz_zErr FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoObj p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objID JOIN Photoz as pz ON pz.objID=s.bestobjid ORDER BY x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
